channel.title: I'm doing an AMA for a YouTube Video
channel.description:
*original idea alert* Well, I haven't made a video in a while, and I figured I'd get back into it by doing an **AMA**.
Ask Me Anything. It can be music related, Auxy related, or just completley random and out of the blue. I'll pick random questions to use in the video.
Ask questions via Disco, or my twitter. My twitter is [@ActuallyProduk](https://twitter.com/actuallyproduk) and use the hashtag #AskProduk when you tweet me. Thanks!
Tweeting is preferable.

  • What sort of direction do you intend to take your sound in the future
